  startTitle: Intermission
  startDescription: 'After your performance, the host announces a brief intermission.
    The crowd of people move about the room forming cliques and starting discussions.


    You
    have some time on your hands before your next performance. You could explore
    the room for intriguing conversations to be had or have an interesting chance
    encounter. You never know what could happen.


    On the other hand, you could
    play it safe and head straight for the bar. No need to risk getting into an awkward
    situation.'
