  m_text: "You approach the woman sitting at the back table. There is a spread of
    books for purchase. \n\n\"Hello there, dear,\" the woman says as she pulls you
    into an inescapable conversation. She won't stop talking, and you're unable to
    track how much time has passed. You're in too deep now.\n\nThe only way out is
    to buy something to end the conversation. "
